  [Text] Pyongyang, May 7 (KCNA) -- The dear leader Comrade 
Kim Chong-il received a gift from the American Popular 
Revolutionary Alliance of Peru. 
  The visiting secretary of the National Executive Committee 
of 
the Alliance, Javier Pedro, handed the gift to Hwang Chang-yop, 
secretary of the Central Committee of the Workers' Party of 
Korea. 

